  "title": "Aquamarine - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "Aquamarine is a Mineral. It can be obtained from Aquamarine Nodes and Gem Nodes in the Mines (floors 40+), from panning, from a Gem Bird on Ginger Island during rainy days, and from Fishing Treasure Chests. It has a 10% chance to be dropped by a slain Dwarvish Sentry in the Volcano Dungeon. It may occasionally be found in a Garbage Can after the player has reached the bottom of the mines.",
